# RewindAI CLI

`rewind` is the terminal interface for RewindAI, the Git-for-memory workflow built on top of the FastAPI backend.

Install locally:

```bash
pip install -e ./cli
```

Example commands:

```bash
rewind status
rewind branch list
rewind checkout main
rewind log
rewind diff main graphql-exploration
rewind chat
rewind commit -m "Captured API direction changes"
```
